profile:
North Star Coatings is family owned and operated asphalt sealing and repair company specializing in residential and commercial work. Sealing driveways and parking lots in all of true northern Ontario giving everyone a chance to have there asphalt maintained for where ever you might be.
 
We have 3 generations of a asphalt work experience and were committed to quality. We only use the best sealers, asphalt and hot rubber recommended  for your asphalt.

Not your basic sealcoating. North Star Coatings uses Gem Seal polymer-modified sand slurry made for high volume traffic areas. Heavily agitated with 1-6 pounds of sand per gallon to give your asphalt the ultimate protection from deterioration, snow plowing, oil and chemical spills and much more. Slurry is a much thicker, heavier coating than basic oil base seal coat and last 3-5 times longer with beautiful dark matte black finish.
